Included page: .ScenarioLibrary (edit)

These scenarios will be accessible to all test cases in the the FitNesseRoot folder. If you are using a different FitNesseRoot Folder, make sure to copy these files if using any setup scenarios.


Update these variables for your specific test environment


  • Expand
  • Collapse

Variables for Scenarios

Default browser can be FIREFOX or CHROME
variable defined: defaultBrowser=FIREFOX

Default Version can be any supported Appian Version in xx.x format from (21.2 - 23.1)
variable defined: defaultVersion=23.1

Default Locale can be en_US or en_GB
variable defined: defaultLocale=en_US

Default URL should include http or https and /suite (e.g. https://forum.appian.com/suite )
variable defined: defaultUrl=REPLACE_APPIAN_URL

To use out of the box functionality, do not update the scenarios below


  • Expand
  • Collapse

Setup customizable for browser, locale, version, and URL

scenario setup for test script for browser browserType locale location version versionNum url appianUrl
setup with browser @browserType
set appian locale to @location
set appian version to @versionNum
set appian url to @appianUrl
set timeout seconds to 20
set start datetime

setup for test script for browser FIREFOX locale en_US version 23.1 url REPLACE_APPIAN_URL

scenario sample username
setup with CHROME browser
set appian url to https://appiancoe.vuram.com/suite/sites/as_virtualwarehouse
set appian version to 22.3
set appian locale to en_US
login with username @username

scenario Enter Case Details with Deliver To DeliverTo with Short Order Description ShortOrderDescription with Building Building with Dummy Reservation DummyReservation with Product Group Productgroup with IO IO
populate field Deliver To with @DeliverTo
populate field Short Order Description with @ShortOrderDescription
populate field Building with @Building
populate field Product Group with @Productgroup
populate field IO with @IO partially matching picker field suggestion


scenario verify value with Deliver To DeliverTo with Building Building
verify field Deliver To contains @DeliverTo
verify field Building contains @Building

get field Deliver To value
get field Building value

scenario Variable with Deliver To DeliverTo with Building Building with Short Order Description ShortOrderDescription
$max= get field Deliver To value
populate field Short Order Description with $max

scenario click button with SAVE DETAILS SAVEDETAILS
click on button @SAVEDETAILS


variable defined: COMMAND_PATTERN=java -Dlog4j.debug -Dlog4j.configuration=file:\\\${automated.testing.home}\log4j.properties -cp %p %m
classpath: C:\FitNesse/**.jar

script
click on menu ORDER PARTS
Enter Case Details with Deliver To Chennai with Short Order Description Tested with Building Shyamala Towers with Dummy Reservation [1] with Product Group CSBG with IO 1234

populate field Short Order Description with Tested

populate field Product Group with CSBG
populate field IO with 1234 partially matching picker field suggestion

script
verify value with Deliver To Chennai with Building Shyamala Towers

verify field Deliver To contains Chennai

script
